    "longBusinessSummary": "FPT Securities Joint Stock Company, a financial institution, engages in the brokerage, trading, investment advisory, custody, and underwriting of securities primarily in Vietnam. The company offers securities trading, such as stock, bond, derivatives, ETF, covered warrant trading, and securities custody; cash deposit, transfer, withdrawal, margin trading, and cash advance; as well as search advisors, and advisory reports. It also provides various services, including corporate restructuring, securities offering/issuance, business valuation, divestment, and auction advisory; information disclosure advisory and EzIR solution, shareholder meeting advisory and EzGSM solution, annual report advisory, sustainability report advisory, dividend policy advisory, and shareholding management advisory and EzLink solutions; corporate governance reporting advisory, company charter advisory and corporate governance regulations; and business planning, financial forecast, due diligence advisory, and HR management advisory and EzHRM solutions. In addition, the company offers public company registration/de-registration, securities listing registration, securities registration, securities trading registration, public tendering, treasury share trading, equitization, and foreign ownership room advisory. The company was incorporated in 2007 and is headquartered in Hanoi, Vietnam.",
